  automatically terminates, regardless of ongoing activity. Defaults to 3600 seconds (1
  hour). Recommended minimum: 60 seconds. Maximum allowed: 28,800 seconds (8 hours).

- `"traceparent"`: The parent trace information for distributed tracing.

